title: Havent received my RP For the  Star guardian contest
body: All my friends got their RP, but I havent even though I uploaded a screenshot. I got S

replies.body:
Hey there,

I'm gonna need a little bit of extra info from you so that we can sort things out:

+ What are the in-game summoner names of at least 2 of the friends you played with when you got S?

+ What is your in-game summoner name that you submitted?
